Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈需要小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续不能见到小凛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会得禁忌症状而死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师也有禁忌症状吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也接不通  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,处男
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你隐藏了什么事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是小凛的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  小孩意外的很聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  流行性腮腺炎是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为见不到小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这本性丑恶的萝莉控
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉她「处男是M  被骂了会有快感」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为没有小凛  我也很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  要认为小凛早点得流行性腮腺炎是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等成人后  疫苗就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛的情况是疥癣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}得疥癣会死吗  又不是动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不单是九重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  小凛马上就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点…有点舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  比起我来小黑更加擅长说坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青木老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重同学她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想马上就让她转校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,转校什么的不是看父母的情况能简单决定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除父母以外还有谁能决定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重  知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人  九重不可能会这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重期待来学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你强硬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪里了解凛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人懂得什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人…你也是大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我有责任保护凛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手续要在这里完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紧要关头啊  青木老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为年龄接近  没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也还是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人懂得什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不知什么时候变成大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛  想出去的话可以从窗口出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直静静待在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了  我去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去商谈了关于转校的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,转校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这眼睛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么我的声音传达不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:13:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老…师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时我也做了和那些无法饶恕的家伙们一样事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,林志  保护好凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这样想的  但是办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你保护好凛  然后  凛也一定会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是昏过去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,林志受惊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…伤害了林志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,林志本来就有伤痕的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  又做不到让林志孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是做我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我在普通的家庭里成长  普通的升学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常无聊普通的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  不单是九重的事情  宇佐  镜  班上同学的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定做不到真正理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我不想放弃想要理解你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的事情  我也想去理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能顺利的表达出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是九重教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  告诉了我  我一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  想知道的心意并不是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是九重告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青木老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待太长时间  吵醒他也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给镜和宇佐打电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她们很担心你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,握手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:18:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师是让我初次相信了他人的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  老师也相信了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,sol是按住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,印度耍蛇人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师吹得好糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很不擅长吹高音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是呢  老师的不是高音而是低音笛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,处男的那个  最多也就是长笛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青木老师  这里很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  要到何时才会有身为教师的自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  小白的处男调教好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:30.59,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算措词规矩  还是能出色地说坏话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记下来  记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:37.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秋姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真服白井老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没  这是那人的爱的鞭笞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道白井老师也会是情敌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这实在不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  眼镜男和眼镜女意外很相配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宝院老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候把我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的笛子发出了好听的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,间接接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不满足于间接的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  像以前那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.78,0:22:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么  小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了  青木老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为教师的我  看来还不能成为杰出的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小凛真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还好不是直接的接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在间接就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.23,0:22:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定不着急了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然偶尔也会急急忙忙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:23:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随着休息 摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定  会真心到最后
